if exists(select 1 from sys.sysforeignkey where role='FK_MPS_OPST_LOKALNA_S_MPS_DRZA') then
alter table MPS_OPSTINA
delete foreign key FK_MPS_OPST_LOKALNA_S_MPS_DRZA
end if;

alter table MPS_OPSTINA
add constraint FK_MPS_OPST_LOKALNA_S_MPS_DRZA foreign key (DR_IDENTIFIKATOR)
references MPS_DRZAVA (DR_IDENTIFIKATOR)
on update restrict
on delete restrict;
